Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:05.56,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Time and time again my hopes are gone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:11.55,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}It's like a never-ending marathon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:18.19,ed-en,,0,0,1,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I hear voices every night of the ones I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.19,0:24:20.77,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}That I loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.84,0:24:26.28,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I try to find the place where I belong
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:32.77,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Until I do, I guess I'll carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.77,0:24:35.64,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Trapped in every sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.64,0:24:39.16,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Feel like I'm gonna lose my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:41.96,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}My freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.18,0:24:54.50,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Without love, without love, without love...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.64,0:24:59.24,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I played the game of life and had a ball
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.67,0:25:05.28,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Crazy of me to think I had it all
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.36,0:25:12.17,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I kept holdin' on to the power, then lost
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.17,0:25:15.78,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}My freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.30,0:25:24.19,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I guess I have to learn there's no freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.19,0:25:27.13,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Without love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:05.56,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我一次又一次失去希望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:11.55,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}如同一场永无止境的征程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:18.19,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}每个夜晚 都能听到离我而去之人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.19,0:24:20.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}亦我所爱之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.84,0:24:26.28,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我苦苦寻找归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:32.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}若不寻得 决不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.77,0:24:35.64,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}历经千辛万苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.64,0:24:39.16,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}近乎失去理智
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:41.96,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我的自由…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.18,0:24:54.50,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}无爱相随 无爱相随 无爱相随…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.64,0:24:59.24,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我沉浸于人生游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.67,0:25:05.28,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}疯狂地认为自己拥有一切
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.36,0:25:12.17,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我手握大权 而后失去
