Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:43.12,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)\pos(444.43,936)}凯迪尔的农场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔 托尔芬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们从今天开始就是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,来打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给你们同样的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要好好合作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照 托尔芬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我来说一下你们的工作内容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔 你觉得这里是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,森林…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是未来的小麦田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这片森林是我的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它租给你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,租？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对 交给你们来打理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要开垦 耕种这片土地 收获作物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我会以合理的价格买下作物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果购买作物的钱超过了你们自身的价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就自己买下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,自己买下自己…也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,自由…能成为自由身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,靠自己的力量 走正规的程序获得自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们够努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,三年之内或许就能实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,地租就等第一次收获再交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有烦恼和疑问 可以问这个帕提尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他很了解这座农场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是用同样的方法成为了自由人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然身在异乡 会有许多困难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天就看托尔芬干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,长途跋涉一定也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,托尔芬 你要多多关照艾纳尔啊 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 老爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 老爷是怎样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,丹麦都是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的故乡也有奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但奴隶一辈子都是奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的故乡是英格兰北部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,冰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,冰岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,冰岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,砍了挺多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这边全都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这边？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那边不是有条河吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,河这边全都是要砍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,河的…这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老爷不是让你看着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想尽早获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那你去砍远一点的树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要让树倒下的方向垂直于河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是要推到河里运走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 这里有没有午饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是要自己去拿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不 帮工的人等会儿会送来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 还挺周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,饭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 托尔芬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的真的 只有你没干了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那我今晚去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好 去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,去被甩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是那个新来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 应该是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一脸蠢相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,奴隶相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你们好 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,知道 听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那就今晚行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,说了是你们的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这 这么点？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 你有意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人就这么点？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 你是第一次当奴隶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那你记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能吃上饭就不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们这些自由民还特地给你们送饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,首先当然是要表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,「非常感谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你这眼神是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,托尔芬 教教他礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 别伤了马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,居然在午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们搞什么啊 就是来偷懒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是奴隶 也别对他们百依百顺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔 你从后面推
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我在前面拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拉到河边把它们绑成木筏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这棵树要不要多砍几段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这么一头老马 拉不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,树是老爷的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不能擅自砍短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 这不是他们的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一般不会给奴隶用马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且只有这么一头老马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔 把前面抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,饿得嘴里反酸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对饶不了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,居然吃了我的午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,帮工不就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,自己没有田地 只能给老爷当帮佣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就和奴隶差不多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是比上不足比下有余 就欺负我们找安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,托尔芬 你也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可是老爷的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,区区帮工 无权使唤我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要向老爷告状
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,告状只会让他们变本加厉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你就甘心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔 托尔芬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 艾纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,第一天感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老爷 我有事报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 农场里的帮…工…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔 你要报告什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的话 我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你不报告了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,水来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,刚从泉眼打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,冰冰凉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,给我来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,急转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去了深处的泉眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在中午之前收完这一片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老爷居然亲自干活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为富人都不自己干活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是丹人还是英格兰人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,干起活来都是一个样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要我说多少遍啊 奥马尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,干吗啊 我在照你说的做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,用短镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 麦秆要留长一点 留到膝盖的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前教过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,割下来不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,割完麦子就是放牧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,把麦秆留长 是为了给家畜吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你都17岁了 还没记住完整的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不明白每一道工序的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了 我知道好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我流程记得很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,听人说话时要谦虚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个样子 作为立于人上的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好 膝盖下面是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢货 你怎么能这么挥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,麦子会被砍坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.66,zhu,,0,0,0,,留膝盖那么高不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那人谁啊 把老爷气成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是老爷的儿子 奥马尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,父子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,亏我偶尔来帮个忙 你就在这叽叽歪歪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,亏我本来还想帮你 还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,站住 你去哪里 奥马尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,去没有你的地方 臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你今后可是要继承这座农场的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出点责任感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没求你让我继承
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大老爷们居然在这磨磨叽叽磨磨叽叽磨磨叽叽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谁要在这干农活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1276,1060)}我要用剑闯出一片天地啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(417.33,1060)}奥马尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(417.33,1060)}给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去英格兰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就最近 绝对要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不要在这穷乡僻壤待一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要加入克努特王弟殿下的军团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,立下一个又一个战功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷 最近是指什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,最 最近就是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不久后 哈拉尔德国王就会召集援军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得您还是继承农场比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么你都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很担心您…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的 干得漂亮 女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,情况怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我给少爷送吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘 嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,先别去打扰 他们开始第二轮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这下子 咱家也就安稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只要少爷一直来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,您您您这是怎么了 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我家女儿冒犯您了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们打的什么算盘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,穷鬼租地农
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不就是想要老爸的财产吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,和凯迪尔家攀亲戚就能财源滚滚了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这 这怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,女人一个个都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷 我们没有这个意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷 留步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的 一个个都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是老爸的附属品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 待在哪儿都不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,您在做什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上跑马很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们又在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你好好走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去找了那个女人 结果被帮工抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.22,zhu,,0,0,0,,所以在喝闷酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 踩到麦子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 如果跟他们闹 又会被大哥骂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是受不了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真羡慕少爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在这座农场里 可以想干啥就干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们哪里懂我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,生气了？生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,您有烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没闲到有空搭理你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们赶紧回营地睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀哎呀 哎呀哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别气冲冲的啦 您还这么年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 别牵马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,再喝几杯吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚就让咱们聊到天明吧 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,向我们倾诉青春的烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们只是想拿我当下酒菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去 把马放开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老实继承农场不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他不了解战争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是觉得战士很威风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,打仗的人 都是禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧 明天还要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前住的村子 两度被军队袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,英格兰国王的军队 把村里的房子都烧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸和他们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能眼睁睁看着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:23:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,第二次 是丹人的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们借口从英格兰国王的恶政下解救人民
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,实际却是烧杀抢掠 无恶不作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们简直是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,披着人皮的禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 托尔芬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.55,0:25:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,「蛇」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
